query:
SELECT id, strategyId, direction, entryPrice, pnl, isTest, source, createdAt
FROM trades 
WHERE DATE(createdAt) = CURDATE()
AND isTest = 0
AND source = 'webhook'
ORDER BY createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
